---
description: "Rules for working on Prometheus metrics collection"
globs: ["internal/collector/**/*.go"]
---

- Aggregation methods via `getValue()`: max, min, avg, sum
- CSV file prefix constants are defined at the top of `collector.go`
- Report generation entry point: `GenerateReports(cr, dirCfg, collector)`
- CSVs are written to the staging directory; packaging reads from staging and writes to upload
- Mock Prometheus responses in tests using existing test utilities
